@page "/install-guide"

<PageTitle>Install Guide</PageTitle>

<section class="space-y-8">
    <div class="space-y-3">
        <div class="app-chip w-fit">Independent installs</div>
        <h1 class="app-page-title">Install Guide</h1>
        <p class="max-w-3xl text-base leading-8 text-slate-300">
            This page will house the practical steps for getting independent games onto Board, from purchase and download through local transfer and final install.
        </p>
    </div>

    <section class="grid gap-6 lg:grid-cols-3">
        <section class="app-panel p-6">
            <div class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.24em] text-cyan-100/75">1. Get the files</div>
            <h2 class="mt-3 font-display text-2xl font-bold text-white">Purchase and download</h2>
            <p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-7 text-slate-300">
                Start with the independent store or publisher selected by the developer, then download the APK or install package provided for Board players.
            </p>
        </section>
        <section class="app-panel p-6">
            <div class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.24em] text-cyan-100/75">2. Connect your device</div>
            <h2 class="mt-3 font-display text-2xl font-bold text-white">Prepare Board and your computer</h2>
            <p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-7 text-slate-300">
                We will document the exact USB or network steps here, along with any Board-side settings that need to be enabled before an install can begin.
            </p>
        </section>
        <section class="app-panel p-6">
            <div class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.24em] text-cyan-100/75">3. Finish the install</div>
            <h2 class="mt-3 font-display text-2xl font-bold text-white">Verify and launch</h2>
            <p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-7 text-slate-300">
                Final checks, troubleshooting notes, and launch verification steps will live here once the install workflow is fully documented.
            </p>
        </section>
    </section>

    <section class="app-panel p-6">
        <div class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.24em] text-cyan-100/75">Coming next</div>
        <p class="mt-3 max-w-3xl text-sm leading-7 text-slate-300">
            The first version is intentionally a structured placeholder so the new navigation is live now. We can expand this into a full step-by-step guide with screenshots, FAQs, and per-store notes next.
        </p>
    </section>
</section>
